parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The parasitic battery drain can cause the battery to drain completely, leaving the driver stranded, and potentially leading to unsafe situations.
symptoms: the battery warning light is illuminated
the battery cannot hold a charge.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning infotainment system can cause distractions while driving, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The STARLINK 7-inch Multimedia Plus unit gets locked-up

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The random shutdown of the vehicle can cause loss of control, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle shuts down for a second and starts back up without pressing the start button
the steering wheel locks up at highway speeds
taking control of the vehicle away from the driver.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden failure or stalling of the engine can cause the vehicle to lose power and control, increasing the risk of accidents, especially when driving at high speeds.
symptoms: the vehicle experiences a sudden loss of power

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rod bearing can cause the engine to seize or stall, leading to a loss of power and control, which can increase the risk of accidents.
The sudden stalling of the engine without warning can cause the vehicle to lose power and control, increasing the risk of accidents, especially when driving at high speeds.
symptoms: there are no warning lights or indicators.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission to engage 2nd gear can cause loss of power, difficulty accelerating, and potentially lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle fails to shift into 2nd gear
resulting in loss of power and difficulty accelerating.
